Importing a Project

You can use import your configuration details to apply to an existing project in the Cisco UCS ADA.

To import a project, perform the following steps:

 1. In the Project(s)/Domain(s) screen, select the project you wish to import.

 2. Click Import. The following window appears

Figure 2-4 Information Window

 3. Click OK to continue.

Figure 2-5 Import

 4. Enter the Name, select the theatre and click Browse to upload the project file. Then, click Open to import.

Note • The project file must be in a zip format containing the config file in xml format.

 • Password cannot be imported.

 5. Click Save. The imported project appears on the Projects screen.

Note Password cannot be imported.
